With its unique design and casual style, the Vans Old Skool 'Blur Check' sneaker is perfect for everyday wear.

title: Vans Slip-on Shoes Black
description: The Vans Slip-On has been a classic staple in the world of skateboarding for many years. This time, Vans teamed up with one of the most iconic metal bands of all time - Metallica. The result is a shoe that features a black canvas upper with Metallica written across the vamps. The midsole also features an engraved Metallica logo, giving the shoe an extra touch of rock and roll edge. The Slip-On also features a padded collar and signature rubber waffle outsole for ultimate comfort and protection.

title: Vans DSM x Old Skool 'DSM Check'
description: The Vans DSM x Old Skool 'DSM Check' is a must-have sneaker for any casual or streetwear enthusiast. This unique take on the classic Old Skool features a black and white checkerboard canvas upper with Dover Street Market branding placed throughout. The sneaker also sports black suede accents on the toe box, heel, and eyestay, as well as a white leather side stripe and red Vans branding on the midsole. Whether you're hitting the streets or just kicking back, the Vans DSM x Old Skool 'DSM Check' is a great sneaker to add to your rotation.

title: Vans MoMA x ComfyCush Old Skool 'Colorful Checkerboard'
description: The Vans MoMA Comfycush Old Skool ‘Colorful Checkerboard’ is a shoe that is both stylish and comfortable. The canvas upper is lined with moisture-wicking materials, and the iconic checkerboard pattern has been given a multicolored twist. The lateral side panel is inscribed with ‘MoMA’ in oversized lettering, making this a perfect shoe for art lovers. The ComfyCush midsole provides cushioning and support, making this shoe ideal for everyday wear.

title: Vans Bodega x Old Skool LX 'Sub Rosa'
description: Introducing the Vans Bodega x Old Skool LX 'Sub Rosa'! This special edition shoe was created in partnership with streetwear retailer Bodega and features a unique design inspired by ancient Greek mythology. The Sub Rosa is crafted from white canvas with a green rose stem jazz stripe and features a black vulcanized midsole with a green foxing stripe. The all-over red rose print makes this shoe truly one-of-a-kind, and it comes packaged in a custom box with a calendar.

title: Vans Notre x Vault OG Old Skool LX 'Off White'
description: Introducing the Notre x Vault OG Old Skool LX 'Off White' – a joint venture between two of the biggest names in streetwear. This sneaker comes in a monochrome neutral finish, perfect for versatile styling. The hairy suede upper is contrasted with tonal canvas on the medial side panel, and the signature side stripe has been reworked in Notre's signature handshake motif. The low-top rests on an off-white vulcanized rubber midsole, with a vintage license plate at the heel for a final touch of luxury.

title: Vans Supreme x Old Skool Pro 'Logo Pattern - Black'
description: The Supreme x Vans Old Skool ‘Logo Pattern’ is a must-have for any avid sneakerhead. This stylish shoe is taken from a six-piece release that dropped as part of the New York brand’s Fall/Winter 2020 collection. The upper uses a traditional combination of suede and canvas, the latter accented with a leather side stripe and grid-like logo print. A red license plate marked with Supreme branding accents the black rubber midsole. Whether you’re rocking them on the court or just strolling around town, these shoes are sure to turn heads.

title: Vans Supreme x Half Cab Pro '92 'Logo Pattern - Black'
description: The Supreme x Vans Half Cab 'Logo Pattern' is a must-have for any fan of the iconic skate brand. This updated version of the classic Half Cab features a mostly black color scheme, with a grid-like pattern formed by repeating iterations of the Supreme logo. The vulcanized rubber midsole is accented with a red license plate, adding an unexpected pop of color to this otherwise stealthy design.

title: Vans OG Old Skool LX 'Forest Night'
description: The Vans OG Old Skool LX 'Forest Night' is a contemporary take on a classic skate shoe. This shoe, which was originally released in 1977, has been updated with a Forest Night and Cilantro colorway, making it perfect for any skater or casual wearer. The shoe is constructed with a sturdy canvas upper, suede overlays, and a vulcanized midsole, providing both style and comfort. Additionally, the gum rubber outsole ensures excellent traction, while the 'Off The Wall' heel tab adds anauthentic touch.

Vans KITH x Classic Slip-On 'Brown Moroccan Pattern'
description: The Vans KITH x Classic Slip-On 'Brown Moroccan Pattern' is a part of the New York brand's Summer 2020 collection. The sneaker features a traditional canvas upper with elastic gussets and a woven Vans tag on the lateral forefoot. The all-over print is a recurring motif throughout the seasonal range, featuring a multicolor design inspired by Moroccan Zellige tiles. A vulcanized white rubber midsole anchors the low-profile silhouette.

title: Vans Toy Story x Era 'Aliens'
description: The Vans x Toy Story Era 'Aliens' is the perfect way to show your fandom. Featuring an all-over pattern of the Pizza Planet aliens, this shoe is sure to turn heads. And with Buzz and Woody buried in between them, you can rest assured that your favorite characters are never far from your feet. The iconic Toy Story logo appears on the tongue, with Disney and Pixar branding on the insole. So whether you're hitting the streets or taking to the skate park, do it in style with the Vans x Toy Story Era 'Aliens'.

Vans The Simpsons x SK8-HI MTE 2.0 DX 'Mr. Plow'
description: The Simpsons x Vans Sk8-Hi MTE 2.0 DX 'Mr. Plow' is the perfect shoe for those who want to take on the elements in style. The water-resistant textile upper is done in a navy blue finish and features a patch advertising the services of Mr. Plow, Homer Simpson's short-lived side gig. The drop-in UltraCush sockliner provides added comfort, while the rugged lug outsoles and 'Mr. Plow' embroidery on the heel overlay complete the look.

title: Vans The Simpsons x Slip-On Pro 'Bart'
description: The Simpsons x Vans Slip-On Pro 'Bart' is a must-have for any fan of the iconic animated series. This limited-edition shoe features a unique color scheme inspired by Bart Simpson himself. The suede upper is durable and comfortable, and the DURACAP underlays in high-wear areas make this shoe built to last. The Pro Vulc Lite midsole provides superior cushioning and support, while the drop-in PopCush sockliner ensures optimal comfort. The Bart skull-and-crossbones print on the sidewall is the perfect finishing touch to this stylish and functional shoe.

title: Vans The Simpsons x Old Skool 'Moe's Tavern'
description: Moe's Tavern is a Springfield institution and now, you can bring a piece of the bar home with you with these special edition Vans Old Skools. Made in collaboration with The Simpsons, these shoes feature characters from the show on both sides - Homer and Barney on the right shoe and Lenny, Carl and Moe Szyslak on the left. A pink leather side stripe and Moe's Tavern patch on the heel add fun pops of color to this otherwise black and white shoe.

description: Vans and Supreme have been collaborating for over 20 years, and their latest release is the Supreme x Sk8-Hi Pro 'Diamond Plate Brown'. This high-top sneaker is inspired by slip-resistant steel plating, with a suede and canvas upper in a brown colorway. The vulcanized sole and rubber outsole stay true to Vans' 1978 original design, making this shoe both stylish and functional.

title: Vans Supreme x SK8-HI Pro 'Diamond Plate Navy Red'
description: The Supreme x Sk8-Hi Pro 'Diamond Plate Navy Red' is a special edition of the classic Vans sneaker, updated with an industrial-inspired print. The shoes are part of a six-shoe pack, all featuring the same steel plating-inspired pattern. The vulcanized sole and rubber outsole provide excellent traction and durability, while the canvas and suede upper offer a comfortable fit.

title: Vans Supreme x Classic Slip-On Pro 'Diamond Plate Yellow'
description: The much-anticipated Supreme x Vans collection is finally here and it does not disappoint. This six-sneaker pack includes two remixed late-70s Vans icons, the Slip-On and Sk8-Hi, with a pattern inspired by industrial steel plating. The Supreme x Classic Slip-On Pro 'Diamond Plate Yellow' is a low-cut canvas upper with 'Supreme' branding on the lateral. A vulcanized sole with rubber Waffle tread provides a classic feel.

title: Vans Supreme x SK8-HI Pro 'Diamond Plate Black Grey'
description: If you're looking for a stylish and comfortable shoe that can take you from the skate park to the streets, then you need the Vans Supreme x Sk8-Hi Pro 'Diamond Plate Grey'. This shoe is a reimagining of Vans' classic 1978 Sk8-Hi, updated with a modern twist. The upper is made from suede and canvas, with a Diamond Plate print that is inspired by slip-resistant steel plating. 'Supreme' lettering on the sidewall ensures that everyone knows you're wearing the latest collaboration between Vans and NY skate and fashion brand, Supreme. The vulcanized sole provides lasting comfort, while the Waffle tread offers excellent grip.

description: Introducing the Vans Disney x Old Skool 'Mickey'! For Mickey Mouse's 90th anniversary, Vans has teamed up with Disney to release exclusive colorways for adults and children alike. This low top features an all-white canvas upper with the classic white leather stripe on the side. The padded collar ensures comfort, while the Mickey Mouse head in black on the tongue and large Mickey hand coming out of the heel add a touch of fun and whimsy.

title: Vans Disney x Slip-On 'Mickey & Minnie'
description: Celebrate the 90th anniversary of Mickey Mouse with the Vans Disney x Slip-On 'Mickey & Minnie' shoes. These special edition shoes feature a black and white checkerboard upper, side panel flames, a padded collar, and a large Mickey Mouse head printed on the toe box. The vulcanized outsole provides flexibility and superior traction, making these shoes perfect for any activity.

description: Introducing the Vans Disney x Old Skool 'Mickey Mouse Club'! Part of a special collaboration between Vans and Disney to celebrate Mickey Mouse's 90th birthday, this Old Skool sneaker is rendered in black suede and canvas with a red jazz stripe. Mickey Mouse himself is embroidered in yellow on the heels, with a cartoon hidden tribute on the interior. The tongue logo also features Mickey for an extra touch of fun.

title: Vans Supreme x Sid Pro 'White Dalmatian'
description: Looking for a unique twist on a classic Vans silhouette? Check out the Supreme x Sid Pro 'White Dalmatian.' This streetwear-ready low top first debuted in 1995, and was brought back in 2018 via a four-sneaker collab with Supreme. The 'White Dalmatian' is the only one of the four that features a graphic, with a white suede upper speckled with black dots. You'll find Supreme branding on the tongue and OG Vans branding on the side, along with twin piping on the vulcanized midsole for a premium finish.

title: Vans Disney x SK8-HI 'Mickey & Minnie'
description: Introducing the Vans Disney x Sk8-Hi 'Mickey & Minnie'! This women's-exclusive sneaker is perfect for any fan of the classic cartoon characters. Mickey Mouse is featured on the right shoe, greeting his girlfriend Minnie Mouse with flowers. On the left shoe, a series of flower embroideries adds a feminine touch. The rest of the shoe is designed with a pink suede and canvas upper, making it super soft and comfortable to wear. Special-edition packaging incorporates Vans' checkerboard motif with a heritage graphic of Mickey, making this sneaker truly unique.

title: Vans Fear of God x Era 95 DX 'Collection 2 Red'
description: The Fear of God x Era 95 DX 'Collection 2 Red' from renowned designer Jerry Lorenzo and iconic sneaker brand Vans is a must-have for any sneakerhead's collection. This limited edition sneaker features black-and-white branding on the body with red corduroy overlays at the forefoot and heel, adding texture and dimension to the classic silhouette. The shoe sits atop a gum-rubber sole, providing sticky traction and a comfortable ride

title: Vans Fear of God x Slip-On 47 DX 'Collection 2 Red'
description: The Vans Fear of God x Slip-On 47 DX 'Collection 2 Red' was released as part of Vans' second collection with Jerry Lorenzo's Fear of God. The shoe features a black canvas upper stamped with white 'Fear of God' branding and red suede overlays on the toe and heel. A padded ankle collar, 'FOG' branding under the tongue, a white waffle rubber outsole and ‘Off the Wall’ branding on the heel complete the look. This shoe is perfect for anyone who loves clean lines and a minimalistic aesthetic.

title: Vans Opening Ceremony x Old Skool LX 'Glitter Pack'
description: Introducing the Vans Opening Ceremony x Old Skool LX 'Glitter Pack'! This sneaker is rendered with an all-over glitter application in a tonal teal hue, making it perfect for those who love to stand out. Fashioned with leather paneling on the upper, the sneaker also showcases the signature jazz-stripe and waffle outsole as a nod to the sneaker’s original design.

title: Vans Opening Ceremony x Old Skool LX 'Glitter Pack'
description: Vans Opening Ceremony x Old Skool LX 'Glitter Pack' is sure to make you stand out from the crowd with its glittery Lavender Pink finish and contrasting red jazz stripe. The leather sock liner also has a shiny finish for an extra touch of luxury. But don't worry, the vulcanized midsole and waffle traction pattern keeps the signature look intact. So whether you're dressing up for a special occasion or just wanting to add a little sparkle to your everyday look, this sneaker is perfect for you!

title: Vans WTAPS x Authentic Syndicate 'Wings'
description: When it comes to cool, trendy footwear, it doesn't get much better than the Vans WTAPS x Authentic Syndicate 'Wings' shoes. These limited edition kicks come in a beautiful golden hue, with W)TAPS logos appearing around the collar. They're perfect for making a statement, whether you're hitting the streets or the skate park. The high-quality suede upper and UltraCush HD insole provide both style and comfort, while the heightened midsole foxing completes the classic look.

title: Vans Takashi Murakami Slip-On LX ' Skull'
description: Takashi Murakami is a world-renowned Japanese artist who is known for his bright and vibrant colors, as well as his anime and Japanese pop culture influences. The Takashi Murakami Slip-On LX 'Yellow Skull' celebrates his creativity with a canvas upper covered in skull prints, evocative of motifs in his other work. This low-top sneaker also features a classic Vans Slip-On design and a vulcanized sole, making it both stylish and comfortable. The sneaker was released alongside three similarly themed t-shirts, so you can complete the look.

title: Vans The North Face x SK8-HI 46 MTE DX 'Red'
description: Introducing the Vans The North Face x Sk8Hi 46 MTE DX sneaker, the perfect footwear for those cold weather adventures. This high-top sneaker features a weather-resistant black suede upper with red laminate ballistic nylon overlays, making it equipped to handle anything nature throws your way. The UltraCush sockliners and MTE 360 technology work together to keep your feet warm and dry all day long, while the vulcanized lug outsole provides optimal traction on slippery surfaces. Available in multiple colors, the Vans The North Face x Sk8Hi 46 MTE DX sneaker is sure to become your go-to footwear for all those cold weather excursions.

title: Vans Peanuts x SK8-HI 'Charlie Brown Maize'
description: Introducing the Vans Peanuts x Sk8-Hi 'Charlie Brown Maize' shoe! This limited edition sneaker is a must-have for fans of Charlie Brown and the Peanuts gang. The yellow canvas upper is printed with black Charlie Brown graphics, and finished with a coordinating Vans sidestripe. The Sk8-Hi silhouette was designed with skaters in mind, and features a higher collar for added ankle protection. Grab your pair before they're gone!

title: Vans Andres Serrano x Supreme x Chukka Pro 'Blood & Semen'
description: The Vans Andres Serrano x Supreme x Chukka Pro 'Blood and Semen' is a unique and stylish sneaker that is perfect for any fashion-savvy individual. The Serrano print on the canvas upper makes this shoe stand out, while the leather lining adds a touch of luxury. The vulcanized rubber midsole and gum rubber outsole provide great comfort and durability, making this an ideal sneaker for everyday wear.

title: Vans Andres Serrano x Supreme x SK8-HI 'Blood and Semen'
description: The Vans Andres Serrano x Supreme x Sk8-Hi 'Blood and Semen' is a must-have for any Supreme or Vans fan. This limited-edition shoe features a bold and controversial print by acclaimed artist Andres Serrano. The shoe is constructed from high-quality materials, with black suede on the toe, eyelets, heel, and a white Jazz stripe. This is a limited-edition shoe that is sure to turn heads, so don't miss your chance to own a piece of history.

title: Vans Andres Serrano x Supreme x Old Skool 'Blood and Semen'
description: The 'Blood and Semen' Old Skool is a special colorway of the classic Vans sneaker that was released in September 2017 in collaboration with Supreme and artist Andres Serrano. The shoe features Serrano's iconic 'Blood and Semen' artwork on the side panels, with a white Jazz Stripe and black suede on the toe, eyelets, and heel. This limited-edition sneaker is perfect for anyone who loves Supreme, Vans, or unique and stylish sneakers.

title: Vans Thrasher x Slip-On Pro 'Thrasher'
description: Vans and Thrasher teamed up for a collaboration that is sure to get skateboarders psyched. The Vans Thrasher x Slip-On Pro combines the best of both brands, with Vans' UltraCush technology and the iconic Thrasher logo. This shoe is perfect for hitting the skatepark or just cruising around town. The black canvas upper is accented by the red foxing stripe and the Thrasher logo on the toe. Whether you're a seasoned skater or a beginner, the Vans Thrasher x Slip-On Pro is a great choice.

Vans Stussy x Old Skool LX 'Rose'
description: Looking for a stylish and comfortable shoe that will take your outfit to the next level? Check out the Vans Stussy x Old Skool Lx Rose! This exclusive collaborative shoe is the perfect blend of style and comfort, with a dusty rose finish on the suede side-stripes and panels along the vamp and heel. The canvas quarter panel is a clean white, while the signature checkerboard pattern appears on the sockliner. The black foxing stripe is printed with Stussy International branding, adding a touch of streetwear edge to this otherwise classic shoe.

title: Vans Old Skool 'Blue Checkerboard'
description: The Vans Old Skool 'Madder' shoe is a classic skate silhouette with a modern twist. The suede and mesh construction provides durability and breathability, while the Madder Brown hues add a unique touch of style. The padded heel collar protects your feet while skating, and the waffle outsole provides optimal traction.

title: Vans Old Skool 'Black Checkerboard'
description: The all-new Vans Old Skool 'Black Checkerboard' is what you need in your life this season! This style features a black and white checkerboard canvas upper with black suede on the toe, heel, and eyelets. The signature waffle outsole provides superior comfort and traction, making these perfect for all-day wear. Add a touch of vintage style to your wardrobe with the Vans Old Skool 'Black Checkerboard'.

title: Vans Bodega x Half Cab LX 'Return of the Dragon'
description: Bodega and Vans have partnered up to bring you an exclusive colorway of the Half Cab LX sneaker. This limited edition sneaker is inspired by the Year of the Dragon, and features a unique design with pony hair construction, green suede paneling, reptile-textured leather accents, and an actual snakeskin pattern on the sideband. For added comfort, the sneaker has a padded collar and chunky gum sole unit. This is a must-have for any serious sneaker head or fashion enthusiast.

title: Vans Peanuts x Old Skool 'Charlie Brown'
description: Step into summer with the Vans Peanuts x Old Skool 'Charlie Brown' shoes. Bright yellow and black come together to create a eye-catching colorway that is perfect for any season. The canvas upper is both comfortable and durable, while the signature waffle outsole provides grippy traction. Charlie Brown's iconic catchphrase is featured on the tongues, adding a fun pop of personality to this otherwise classic sneaker.

title: Vans Peanuts x Authentic 'Woodstock'
description: Vans and Peanuts are back at it again with the release of the Vans Peanuts x Authentic 'Woodstock' sneaker. This time around, the classic Authentic silhouette gets a makeover with an all-over print of Woodstock, the beloved Peanuts character. The shoe is finished off with white eyelets, a white vulcanized midsole, and a waffle gum rubber outsole for added grip and durability.

title: Vans Peanuts x SK8-Hi Reissue 'Snoopy Bones'
description: The Vans Peanuts x SK8-Hi Reissue 'Snoopy Bones' sneaker is a stylish and versatile sneaker that is perfect for both casual and athletic wear. Featuring a black and white canvas upper with classic Peanuts illustrations, this sneaker is sure to turn heads wherever you go. The original autoclave construction and grippy rubber tread provide superior comfort and support, making this sneaker ideal for skating or simply running errands around town.

title: Vans Anti Social Social Club x Dover Street Market x Authentic LX 'White'
description: The Anti Social Social Club x Dover Street Market x Vans Authentic LX celebrates the launch of Dover Street Market's global retailer in Singapore. The debut of this 'White' version in May 2017 features a custom canvas upper with text-branded laces and contrast grid stitching. Striped foxing tape and Neek Lurk's 'Get Weird' slogan update the vulcanized midsole. A retro-inspired license plate on the heel and a Waffle outsole complete the look of this classic sneaker.

title: Vans Anti Social Social Club x Dover Street Market x SK8-HI 'Black'
description: The Anti Social Social Club x Dover Street Market x Vans Sk8-Hi is a limited edition sneaker created to celebrate the launch of Dover Street Market's Singapore store. Designed by ASSC founder Neek Lurk, the shoe features a black canvas upper with wordmarks on the laces, contrast stitching, and a leather sidestripe. The classic midsole picks up tonal foxing tape and 'Get Weird' text, while a license plate on the heel and a Waffle outsole complete the look.

description: The NEIGHBORHOOD x Mister Cartoon x Vans Old Skool 36 DX ‘Tokyo Los Angeles’ is the perfect blend of East meets West. This limited edition sneaker is a tribute to the two cities that have been integral to the brand's DNA. The monochromatic black suede upper with tonal leather side stripes and custom ‘Tokyo’ and ‘Los Angeles’ embroidery on the toe box of the right and left shoe give this shoe a clean look that is sure to turn heads. On the back, ‘Uncle Toons Mart’ and ‘By NEIGHBORHOOD’ adorns each heel panel, adding a touch of fun.

description: Looking for a stylish and comfortable pair of shoes that can keep up with your active lifestyle? Check out the Vans Supreme x Grosso Mid Monogram S shoes. These versatile sneakers are perfect for skating, biking, or just hanging out with friends. The red suede upper and all-over print of the Supreme ‘S’ logo give these shoes a unique and eye-catching look, while the vulcanized rubber midsole provides cushioning and support.

title: Vans Supreme x Era 'Monogram S - Red'
description: When it comes to skate shoes, there are few brands more iconic than Vans. The Supreme x Vans Era 'Red' is a must-have for any skateboarder or shoe enthusiast. This shoe is part of the 'Monogram S' pack and features a two-tone print upper, white leather lining, and PopCush insole for added comfort. The vulcanized midsole and gum rubber outsole provide superior grip and durability, while the red license plate adds a touch of style.

title: Vans Chukka Low Sidestripe Red

description: The Vans Supreme x Era Monogram S in black is a must-have sneaker for any fan of the iconic brands. This low-top style features a printed canvas upper with a padded collar, white leather lining, and Vans' PopCush insole for impact protection and a smooth ride. The red "Off the Wall" license plate and vulcanized white rubber midsole complete the look of this versatile and stylish sneaker.

title: Vans Kith x Vault OG Classic Slip-On LX 'Gray Tile'
description: In celebration of Ronnie Fieg's 10th anniversary, Kith has teamed up with Vans to release a special edition capsule collection. The Kith x Vans Vault OG Classic Slip-On LX 'Gray Tile' is a must-have for any sneakerhead or fashion enthusiast. The unique all-over print on the canvas upper is eye-catching and sure to turn heads. The comfortable fit and easy on/off design make the shoes perfect for everyday wear. The red license plate at the heel is a nice pop of color that adds a bit of contrast to the overall look. The Vans branding on the sockliner and the anniversary-themed 'KXTH' logo complete the design of these special edition shoes.

title: Vans Kith x Vault OG Classic Slip-On LX 'Multi Tile'
description: Ronnie Fieg’s highly anticipated 10th anniversary collection with Vans Vault is finally here, and it does not disappoint. The Kith x Vans Vault OG Classic Slip-On LX ‘Multi Tile’ is a standout from the collection, with its eye-catching canvas upper covered in a series of abstract geometric prints. traditional Vans logo tab adorns the lateral side, but with mismatched branding on the interior side for a fun twist. Underfoot, you’ll find Vans’ signature waffle-traction outsole in tacky gum rubber – perfect for keeping you grounded whether you’re hitting the streets or the skate park.

title: Vans Kith x Vault OG Classic Slip-On LX 'Floral'
description: To celebrate its 10th anniversary, New York-based retailer Kith has teamed up with Vans Vault on a special capsule collection. The Vans Kith x Vault by Slip-On OG Classic is a striking sneaker that features an eye-catching floral design. The shoes are crafted from a durable canvas material and rest on a comfortable rubber sole, making them ideal for everyday wear. The sockliner isbranded with Vans logos and the commemorative ‘KXTH’ logo, adding a stylish finishing touch to this must-have shoe.

title: Vans Kith x Vault OG Classic Slip-On 'Multi Tile'
description: In celebration of their 10-year anniversary, New York-based retailer Kith has teamed up with Vans Vault to release an expansive collection of Slip-Ons. This 'Multi Tile' colorway is one of the most eye-catching in the bunch, with a subtle multicolor print applied to the canvas upper. Elastic gore detailing and a woven Vans tab on the lateral side add some nice finishing touches, while a contrasting white midsole provides a contrast against the colorful upper. A standard waffle traction outsole in grippy gum rubber completes the look.

title: Vans Kith x Vault OG Classic Slip-On 'Bandana Multi'
description: The Vans Vault Classic Slip-On x Kith TD is a special edition shoe from the 10-year anniversary collection of Ronnie Fieg's retail empire and brand. This shoe features a multicolor bandana print on the canvas upper, with elastic gore detailing for easy on and off. The sockliner includes traditional Vans branding, as well as a special 'KXTH' logo. The low-top is mounted on a vulcanized rubber midsole, and the outsole features a waffle-tread gum rubber for added support and traction.

Vans Kith x Vault OG Classic Slip-On LX 'Floral'
description: To celebrate its 10th anniversary, New York-based retailer Kith has teamed up with Vans Vault on a special capsule collection. The Vans Kith x Vault by Slip-On OG Classic is a striking sneaker that features an eye-catching floral design. The shoes are crafted from a durable canvas material and rest on a comfortable rubber sole, making them ideal for everyday wear. The sockliner isbranded with Vans logos and the commemorative ‘KXTH’ logo, adding a stylish finishing touch to this must-have shoe.

title: Vans Kith x Vault OG Classic Slip-On 'Multi Tile'
description: In celebration of their 10-year anniversary, New York-based retailer Kith has teamed up with Vans Vault to release an expansive collection of Slip-Ons. This 'Multi Tile' colorway is one of the most eye-catching in the bunch, with a subtle multicolor print applied to the canvas upper. Elastic gore detailing and a woven Vans tab on the lateral side add some nice finishing touches, while a contrasting white midsole provides a contrast against the colorful upper. A standard waffle traction outsole in grippy gum rubber completes the look.

title: Vans Kith x Vault OG Classic Slip-On 'Bandana Multi'
description: The Vans Vault Classic Slip-On x Kith TD is a special edition shoe from the 10-year anniversary collection of Ronnie Fieg's retail empire and brand. This shoe features a multicolor bandana print on the canvas upper, with elastic gore detailing for easy on and off. The sockliner includes traditional Vans branding, as well as a special 'KXTH' logo. The low-top is mounted on a vulcanized rubber midsole, and the outsole features a waffle-tread gum rubber for added support and traction.
